{"tid":1921853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國曼谷出現集體感染 當局懷疑源頭來自港人","createTime":"2020-03-12T08:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T05:59:54.000Z","uid":21470,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9faebc182bbfb1ed43d2e828b3e036ea01ec6b","tid":1921853,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"泰國曼谷出現集體感染 當局懷疑源頭來自港人<br />\n<br />\n泰國急增11人確診病例，累計增至70人。衛生部說，這11名患者，早前出席一個15人的聚會，懷疑病毒源頭是席間一名香港人，他已經回港，未知是否確診，相信是泰國至今發現的最大宗集體感染個案。報道指，聚會二月下旬在曼谷通羅地區一間餐廳舉行，出席的多名年輕人，曾經共用一隻杯來分享飲品，又吸食同一枝煙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273215&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1273215%26csid%3D261_341&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=15fc0cd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273215&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"67a8c698c616b7baf0fbfe7b721b2832caf224ad","tid":1921853,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"仲要係年輕人"},{"pid":"0cb40d79b1a578a2e6f1eee38b28dd7e777e926c","tid":1921853,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 社區大爆發"},{"pid":"c841e48c4434d50b2a2c31b3d8c3d95c2d678c7a","tid":1921853,"uid":229185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hk